&lt;li&gt;It is virtually impossible for a team without clear boundaries to succeed&lt;br /&gt;
 对于没有明确界限的团队来说，这几乎是不可能成功的&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;But if you lock people into a team only mindset, they can overlook environmental changes around them&lt;br /&gt;
