&lt;h2 id=&#34;legitimate-authority-must-be-granted-to-the-team-必须授予团队合法权限&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#legitimate-authority-must-be-granted-to-the-team-必须授予团队合法权限&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Legitimate authority must be granted to the team 必须授予团队合法权限&lt;/h2&gt;
