&lt;h1 id=&#34;manage-quality-管理质量&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#manage-quality-管理质量&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Manage Quality 管理质量&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The process of translating the quality management plan into executable activities…&lt;br /&gt;
 将质量管理计划转换为可执行活动的过程…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The values of this process are that it increases the probability of meeting the (project’s) quality objectives as well as identifying ineffective processes and causes of poor quality.&lt;br /&gt;
 此过程的价值在于，它增加了达到（项目的）质量目标以及确定无效的过程和质量低下的原因的可能性。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;quality-metrics-质量指标&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#quality-metrics-质量指标&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Quality Metrics 质量指标&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A description of a project or product and how to measure it.&lt;br /&gt;
 项目或产品的描述以及如何衡量。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Metrics are meaningless without context; we give context to metrics by applying SMART goals to them&lt;br /&gt;
 没有环境，指标就毫无意义。我们通过将 SMART 目标应用于指标来为它们提供环境&lt;/p&gt;
