&lt;p&gt;Acceptable range of estimates (e.g. +/- 10%)&lt;br /&gt;
 可接受的估算范围（例如 +/- 10％）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;cost-estimate-成本估算&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#cost-estimate-成本估算&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Cost estimate 成本估算&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;p. 241&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;defined-定义&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#defined-定义&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; defined 定义&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“A quantitative assessment of the likely costs for resources required to complete the activity.  It is a prediction that is based on the information that is available at a given point in time.”&lt;br /&gt;
 完成活动所需资源的可能成本的定量评估。这是基于给定时间点可用信息的预测。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;should-consider&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#should-consider&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; should consider&lt;/h2&gt;
