 权衡取舍&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Risks&lt;br /&gt;
 风险性&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Generally expressed in currency amount (USD, rupees, yen, euros, etc.)&lt;br /&gt;
 通常以货币金额（美元，卢比，日元，欧元等）表示&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;will&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#will&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; will…&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Typically improve as the project continues (-25% to +75% =&amp;gt; -5% to +10%)&lt;br /&gt;
 通常随着项目的进行而改善（-25％至 + 75％=&amp;gt; -5％至 + 10％）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The expectation of the level of accuracy will tend to become more exacting&lt;br /&gt;
 对准确性水平的期望将趋于更加严格&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
